<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Happy Birthday Titi❤️</title>

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff758c, #ff7eb3);
  text-align: center;
  color: white;
}

.container {
  padding: 20px;
}

h1 {
  margin-top: 20px;
}

.hearts button {
  font-size: 28px;
  padding: 12px 18px;
  margin: 10px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 50%;
  cursor: pointer;
  background: white;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.hearts button:hover {
  transform: scale(1.2);
}

.card {
  display: none;
  margin-top: 20px;
  background: white;
  color: #333;
  padding: 15px;
  border-radius: 15px;
  width: 90%;
  max-width: 350px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}

.card img {
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 12px;
}

.line {
  margin-top: 10px;
  font-size: 17px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<h1>Happy Birthday Dharru 💝</h1>

<p>
Happy birthday, sweetu. I hope your special day is as special as you are to me,  
and as special as I am to you!  
<br><br>
Happy birthday to one who warms my heart 💖
</p>

<h3>Click here on heart ❤️</h3>

<div class="hearts">
  <button onclick="showCard(1)">💖</button>
  <button onclick="showCard(2)">💗</button>
  <button onclick="showCard(3)">💘</button>
</div>

<!-- CARD 1 -->
<div id="card1" class="card">
  <img src="photo1.jpg">
  <div class="line">To my best friend: Thank you for being my rock and my safe space. Through thick and thin, our bond remains unbreakable. I'm so lucky to have you in my life</div>
</div>

<!-- CARD 2 -->
<div id="card2" class="card">
  <img src="photo2.jpg">
  <div class="line">Every moment with you feels like a beautiful dream</div>
</div>

<!-- CARD 3 -->
<div id="card3" class="card">
  <img src="photo3.jpg">
  <div class="line">
  Happy birthday Dhara💞 May your day be filled with everything you love most (I know it's me 😚).
  </div>
</div>

</div>

<script>
function showCard(num) {
  document.getElementById("card1").style.display = "none";
  document.getElementById("card2").style.display = "none";
  document.getElementById("card3").style.display = "none";

  document.getElementById("card" + num).style.display = "block";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
